  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析总结**：\n\n1. **主要错误模式**：所有frontend服务都报告相同的错误 - `failed to get ads: rpc error: code = Unknown desc =`\n\n2. **根因识别**：adservice服务出现了注入异常，具体是Byteman代理触发了名为`AdService-getRandomAds-exception-1749532239`的规则，导致在`getRandomAds()`方法中抛出`java.lang.Error: Injected error`\n\n3. **影响范围**：所有frontend实例（frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2）都无法正常获取广告服务，错误出现频次高达3001次\n\n4. **故障类型**：这是一个典型的服务级故障，adservice由于异常注入机制导致服务不可用，进而影响依赖它的frontend服务正常运作。\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\nBased on the metric analysis, I can now provide a detailed analysis of the fault. Let me examine the key indicators and identify the root cause.\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"node_filesystem_free_bytes\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"pod_processes\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in error_ratio and client_error_ratio metrics indicating service degradation\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio p99 increased from 0.0 to 0.56 (200% change), client_error_ratio p99 increased from 0.0 to 0.56 (200% change)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Major latency spike in rrt_max metric affecting service performance\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max p99 increased from 76359.18 to 9218.28 (156.91% change), median rrt_max increased by 14.71%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Severe latency degradation in rrt_max metric impacting service responsiveness\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max p99 increased from 9837.6 to 69115.28 (150.16% change), median rrt_max increased by 10.98%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-04\",\n      \"reason\": \"Node-level memory usage reduction indicating potential resource pressure or cleanup\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_usage_rate decreased from 34.22% to 29.87% (13.56% reduction), p99 decreased by 43.47%\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## Analysis Summary\n\nThe fault analysis reveals several key issues:\n\n**Primary Service Issues:**\n1. **adservice-0**: Shows critical error ratio spikes (200% increase) indicating service degradation\n2. **currencyservice-1**: Experienced significant latency spikes (156.91% p99 increase)\n3. **emailservice-0**: Severe latency degradation (150.16% p99 increase)\n\n**Node-Level Observations:**\n- **aiops-k8s-04**: Memory usage reduction suggests potential resource reclamation or cleanup activities\n- **aiops-k8s-06** and **aiops-k8s-08**: Minor filesystem and memory changes, likely secondary effects\n\n**Key Findings:**\n- The fault appears to be primarily service-level rather than infrastructure-level\n- Multiple services show latency degradation, suggesting a cascading effect\n- No significant pod restarts or process changes detected (`pod_processes` stable)\n- Memory and filesystem metrics show minor fluctuations but no critical resource exhaustion\n\nThe most critical issues are the error ratio spikes in adservice-0 and latency degradation in currencyservice-1 and emailservice-0, which likely contributed to the overall system fault.\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\n基于获取到的调用链数据，我来分析故障的根因。让我仔细分析异常调用链和延迟模式。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice的EmptyCart操作延迟从正常2.4秒激增至31.9秒，延迟倍数13.1倍，是调用链中最严重的延迟\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"redis的HMSET操作延迟从正常1.7秒激增至31.1秒，延迟倍数18.8倍，表明cartservice依赖的redis出现严重性能问题\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"paymentservice的Charge操作延迟从正常12.8秒激增至80.4秒，延迟倍数6.3倍，是checkout流程中的关键瓶颈\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice的PlaceOrder操作延迟从正常154-159秒激增至355-339秒，延迟倍数2.1-2.2倍，是上游服务延迟的受害者\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 分析总结\n\n**故障根因分析**：\n\n1. **主要根因**：**Redis数据库性能严重下降**，导致cartservice的EmptyCart操作延迟激增18.8倍，这是整个调用链中最严重的延迟问题。\n\n2. **次要根因**：**paymentservice响应缓慢**，Charge操作延迟增加6.3倍，进一步加剧了checkout流程的延迟。\n\n3. **传播路径**：\n   - Redis性能问题 → cartservice延迟 → checkoutservice延迟 → frontend延迟\n   - paymentservice延迟 → checkoutservice延迟 → frontend延迟\n\n4. **关键发现**：\n   - 所有异常都集中在checkout流程中，特别是PlaceOrder操作\n   - 多个frontend实例都受到影响，表明问题具有系统性\n   - 虽然status_code显示为2（正常），但延迟指标表明存在严重的性能问题\n\n**建议**：优先检查Redis集群的健康状态和资源使用情况，同时监控paymentservice的性能指标。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_hypothesis": "adservice-0 is the root cause due to Byteman agent injecting exceptions in getRandomAds() method, causing rpc errors and service degradation"}
